**1.Upload Dataset**

# Install Kaggle API
!pip install -q kaggle

# Install unzip tool
!apt-get -qq install -y unzip

# Create Kaggle directory
!mkdir -p ~/.kaggle

# Move kaggle.json credentials file into the Kaggle directory
!cp kaggle.json ~/.kaggle/

# Set correct permissions for kaggle.json
!chmod 600 ~/.kaggle/kaggle.json

# Download the dataset from Kaggle using its dataset identifier
!kaggle datasets download -d haaroonafroz/material-dataset-new

# Extract the downloaded ZIP file into the dataset_raw folder
!unzip -q material-dataset-new.zip -d dataset_raw



